                     <interp inst="t17680907-20-person238" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live in the Borough, and keep an upholstery warehouse; I came from Leeds, I have known him from a child, and since he has been in town he was always a very civil honest young man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17680907-20-person239">
                  John 
                  Wilkinson 
               <interp inst="t17680907-20-person239" type="surname" value="Wilkinson"></interp>
