                     <interp inst="t17680907-20-person239" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live in Black-friars, I belong to the Custom-house, I am a Yorkshire-man, I have known him ever since he came to town, he brought a letter of recommendation to me as a very sober honest young man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17680907-20-person240">
                  Robert 
                  Althwaite 
