                     <interp inst="t17680907-20-person240" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a rope-maker, I have known him nine years and a half, he has the character of a very sober industrious man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17680907-20-person241">
                  Henry 
                  Farrer 
               <interp inst="t17680907-20-person241" type="surname" value="Farrer"></interp>
